## 📌 Insights

- **Single carriageways** account for the most casualties (309.7K)
- **Cars** are involved in nearly 80% of all casualties
- **Dry road surfaces** see more accidents (279,445) than wet (115,261)
- **Urban areas** have slightly more casualties than rural
- **Daytime accidents** (305K) outnumber dark-condition ones (112.9K)

